Title: Object: A View of the City & Port of Alexandria & Isle of Pharos
Object: Ancient History
Description: A view of the city of Alexandria, the harbour and the island of Pharos with its lighthouse to the foreground, the royal palace and theatre marked in the town, the harbour with numerous ships, a key below, plate to a later British edition of Rollin's "Histoire Ancienne", bound in a book of plates to that work Engraving and etching
Producer name: Print made by: William Henry Toms
Curator's comments: Bound in a book of plates to Rollin's Ancient History. The images catalogued under 1873,0510.1-86.
